modules.description: Converts numbers to fixed-length binary strings, pads or truncates as needed. Handles operations on byte sequences for file writing, including endianness conversion. Supports extracting and setting individual bits within a byte.

Converts integers to bit lists, pads them to a specified length, and maps bit sequences to byte arrays. Handles endianness conversion for integers into byte lists and writes raw bit data to binary files. Processes specific integer-to-byte transformations for fixed-size representations.
